import classes from './admin_styles/patient_item.module.css' function Patient_Entry(props){ let {first_name, middle_name, last_name, birth_date, phone_number, email_address, street_address_line1, street_address_line2, city, state, zip_code, photo_path, appointment_date, appointment_time} = props.post; const formattedBirthDate = new Date(birth_date).toLocaleDateString('en-US', { day: 'numeric', month: 'long', year: 'numeric' }); const formattedApptDate = new Date(appointment_date).toLocaleDateString('en-US', { day: 'numeric', month: 'long', year: 'numeric', }); const formattedApptTime = new Date(appointment_time).toLocaleDateString('en-US', { hour: 'numeric', minute: 'numeric' }); return(

{first_name}

{middle_name}

{last_name}

{formattedBirthDate}

{phone_number}

{email_address}

{street_address_line1}

{street_address_line2}

{city}

{state}

{zip_code}

{photo_path}

{formattedApptDate}

{formattedApptTime}

) } export default Patient_Entry;
